<div class="row hide-on-embed">
  <div class="col-lg-12">
    <h1 class="page-header">Welcome!</h1>
    <p>Using the map below, select a marker to learn more about it or select samples from the menu to the left.</p>
    <p>You can use the drawing tools inside the map pane to select and compare multiple markers at once</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">EPA AirNow Air Quality Forecasts (for 50 miles from the center of the map)</div>
            <div class="panel-body" style="padding:10px; overflow:scroll; max-height: 93px; min-height: 93px;">
                <div id="home-map-aqis-container"><p>Loading... please wait </p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="home-map-container">
            <div class="map home-map" id="map_canvas" style="width:100%;height:680px;"></div>
            <hr />
            <div class="alert alert-info">
                Looking for mobile bike sensor data? We're working on a way to better visualize it.
                <br />
                See our work in progress <a href="http://recordit.co/ivXsuzmtaz" target="blank" title="screencast of data visualization of bike data"  class="alert-link">here</a> and <a href="http://recordit.co/f3ktmGd95W" target="blank" title="screencast of data visualization of bike data" class="alert-link">here</a>. Feedback is always welcome.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="text-right">
            <%= erb :_share_tools %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <%= erb :_map_filters %>
    </div>
</div>
